<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<opml version="1.0" xmlns:sx="http://www.microsoft.com/schemas/rss/sse"><head><title>The Path of a Spiritual Warrior</title><dateCreated>2024-01-27T13:18:16</dateCreated><dateModified>2025-08-05T22:32:17</dateModified><ownerName>cloudobserver@gmail.com</ownerName></head><body><outline text="Are you ready for annihilation?"><outline text="It's the nature of the world to have many problems."><sx:sync version="1" id="o0cC6nXFkUGahrJWNzLVBA==" /></outline><outline text="Despite these problems, we search the world for happiness. Anyway it's not a sin to wander all over the world searching for happiness. It takes a long time to realize the self-centered pleasures of the world are not, in fact, very satisfying."><sx:sync version="1" id="WW39WzBya0ujIZqEej3mRQ==" /></outline><outline text="In the high income countries, we have tried everything the world has to offer.  After all that, we may come to realize that something is missing. What is the purpose of this existence? Is there something more?"><sx:sync version="1" id="mM3PQuiB80GvpqjvFNnaOg==" /></outline><outline text="Maybe, by some twist of fate, something happens to you. The synchronicity of the Universe gives you a glimpse of something beyond. It may be subtle, it may overwhelming, but something will awaken the dormant spirituality that is within you. Then you want to return to that feeling at all costs. It is too painful to sink back into negativity, intellectual games, or what have you. You experience a burning desire to be free."><sx:sync version="1" id="Jv3FyttpykCR4emA44ZBdQ==" /></outline><outline text="If you are lucky, this desire will increase until it fills your heart and soul. In the best case scenario, you will be crying tears of anguish, day and night, with unbearable longing for your Supreme Beloved."><sx:sync version="1" id="4TYYi/sfOUmANUsA8zOJfw==" /></outline><outline text="The thing is, your old self, your old belief system has to be annihilated."><sx:sync version="1" id="OasIbHcEMEylYNG25HmOYw==" /></outline><outline text="You have to transcend and dissolve the ego and false sense of self."><sx:sync version="1" id="0Dxs0XOZI0usrpyteDpa2A==" /></outline><outline text="This sounds dangerous because it is.  You need the grace of a Spiritual Master."><sx:sync version="1" id="I3jn+8FY3UCpSHUwFl01zw==" /></outline><outline text="Don't worry. If you cry with sincere and all-consuming longing, continuously, you will somehow find your Master. It's a law of the Universe."><sx:sync version="1" id="l+ZfEp78wUKNlSeysoLnwg==" /></outline><outline text="Do you want to be annihilated?"><outline text="Most people will find this path threatening and extreme."><sx:sync version="1" id="ASerIIdPoE2vygjBm+EPIg==" /></outline><outline text="They say it's crazy to let go of all forms of security, including ego, possessions, and body."><sx:sync version="1" id="ROh0vkhjs06/MukQFf5iXg==" /></outline><outline text="They say there is no future for people who live in the eternal now."><sx:sync version="1" id="e1Cf9l1vZEWOz7WRwW1Lpw==" /></outline><outline text="If you are ready to pour your heart and soul into an all-out assault on your inner and outer demons, you are already on the Path of the Spiritual Warrior."><sx:sync version="1" id="YvtapmLSLUe6lrUzy4s6oQ==" /></outline><outline text="I salute you as a fellow traveler on this golden road."><sx:sync version="1" id="mEMuhDefNUO8oCd29xjVDw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="7MWIJ6x4jkaMMmE7b49WjA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="x7idXWlToE2Sx8J3spYOBg==" /></outline><outline text="We exist in multiple dimensions"><outline text="We are multi-dimensional beings. Each of us exists in a limited physical body, as a temporary resident on the earth. At the same time, each person exists as pure spirit, an eternal being, one with the Infinite. "><sx:sync version="1" id="OIOVPPE1YEyhbdFkuzfW+w==" /></outline><outline text="Both of these realities are valid but they contradict each other. It’s the weirdest thing."><sx:sync version="1" id="K/DnxFGzRkmcl0dmI9S1Jw==" /></outline><outline text="So we live in two worlds at once. In the physical world, the soul is completely identified with the body and is concerned with staying alive and so many activities. The incarnated soul experiences an endless series of thoughts, needs, and problems. Important stuff. People may suffer and die. You may suffer and die."><sx:sync version="1" id="n0gvmDSMIEurdb1svRdgLQ==" /></outline><outline text="Simultaneously the soul is pure consciousness that is perfect and complete. There is pure blissful awareness inside you that is beyond this world, in which you know there are no problems anywhere. Everything is perfect as it is."><sx:sync version="1" id="5m9+7rbESkGJxB48Tg62tw==" /></outline><outline text="The blissful experience may last for a few minutes, hours, or more. In most cases, this vision dissipates and you find yourself once again stuck in the problems of material reality, especially the mental problems."><sx:sync version="1" id="LX/RGK0StkaaCIfidDOavg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="M+/iSUk3t0W1oWSa1qIgrA==" /></outline><outline text="Paradoxes of being a spiritual being in a material world"><outline text="✨ Paradoxes that we face ✨"><sx:sync version="1" id="j12TNIMEmE2i/lMVqsDq4Q==" /></outline><outline text="Physical World  ↔️  Spirit World"><sx:sync version="1" id="otF5tfkiQEW+0GEV2O1YBQ==" /></outline><outline text="Temporary  ↔️ Eternal"><sx:sync version="1" id="zBy1uc2BoEyjINp5/f7alA==" /></outline><outline text="Logical  ↔️  Unexplainable"><sx:sync version="1" id="9gsxapJiQUalvIc42O7hiQ==" /></outline><outline text="Good &amp; bad  ↔️  All good"><sx:sync version="1" id="kIXjBNYq+kC/ieyy0qIfFA==" /></outline><outline text="Unsatisfying  ↔️  Blissful"><sx:sync version="1" id="Q2xNz2TuA0iwNQ8JBJh81Q==" /></outline><outline text="At risk  ↔️  Invincible"><sx:sync version="1" id="x1Vtd5StHkWWQQtn7bSK2A==" /></outline><outline text="Separation  ↔️  Oneness"><sx:sync version="1" id="xZh9i6OZc0CGnh6ruW18+Q==" /></outline><outline text="Limitations &amp; scarcity  ↔️  Complete security"><sx:sync version="1" id="vybR2/wLqki3cP9bsTEYTQ==" /></outline><outline text="Action &amp; Doing  ↔️  Pure witness &amp; Not doing"><sx:sync version="1" id="l56u/Bm6mU2J+2a1+Fwc6g==" /></outline><outline text="There are many  ↔️  There is only one"><sx:sync version="1" id="r+OiPGOUVEOc0UOpVYl9UQ==" /></outline><outline text="Hatred has power  ↔️  Love is the only power"><sx:sync version="1" id="N0aRe1Yx/EWEhrJk8l/EEQ==" /></outline><outline text="Narrow consciousness  ↔️  All-knowing consciousness"><sx:sync version="1" id="DdneCtRzfE+5RBv/2pAttQ==" /></outline><outline text="Problems everywhere  ↔️  Perfection that includes all imperfection"><sx:sync version="1" id="9Udlh80pKUenQZc1e12TxA==" /></outline><outline text="How can you and I make sense of an existence with these inherent contradictions?"><sx:sync version="1" id="LaxPORdRFkiGMRWYLIqQ2w==" /></outline><outline text="How can we live as spiritual beings in a material world?"><sx:sync version="1" id="nIPvvgvD/0yvzRLBtad5Dw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="ojBRhUe2h0KyMXqmAUFzgw==" /></outline><outline text="Love is all that matters"><outline text="Your job is to manifest love at all times. Everything else is secondary to that."><sx:sync version="1" id="PQcgN8Xr+0GhQKC59psCvw==" /></outline><outline text="And yet you are not required to do your job. You are free to follow any path. You are free to make mistakes and perform selfish actions. You are free to become lost in negativity. Regardless, your experiences will gradually lead you back to your true purpose."><sx:sync version="1" id="BqIJSXNy8kCmNZr0uDPm0A==" /></outline><outline text="You are called on to give your best to the world, using your unique and unexpected abilities."><sx:sync version="1" id="4ahX4A+Qrk2Bxz7c3NkRRA==" /></outline><outline text="You have complete authority over your actions and thoughts. No one can tell you, &quot;You're not doing it right&quot;."><sx:sync version="1" id="Cknlt5zUn0iFcN4cfptxEg==" /></outline><outline text="The word &quot;Love&quot; does not convey the dimensions of Supreme Love:"><outline text="Pure awareness"><sx:sync version="1" id="0rONmobXaU2QgXanGUKgrQ==" /></outline><outline text="Infinite compassion"><sx:sync version="1" id="6qHBFv1vMkG09YZzjn/rVg==" /></outline><outline text="Divine Intelligence"><sx:sync version="1" id="UW6D6Hl8FEuIXJEkULSaKA==" /></outline><outline text="Unlimited creativity and enthusiasm"><sx:sync version="1" id="bV5wORviUUOESz497/qlxw==" /></outline><outline text="Child-like joy and wonder"><sx:sync version="1" id="1gkbvKx2NkyGkL1d4MsmnQ==" /></outline><outline text="Unconditional devotion"><sx:sync version="1" id="rAKETk30j0KyWFUtynxzkw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="sEIlW8R3QEix1Ovziil0jA==" /></outline><outline text="Most important point"><outline text="You are loved, cherished, and protected by this multi-dimensional love."><sx:sync version="1" id="1Re028GFPE2KmXTThErapg==" /></outline><outline text="There never was a time when this was not so."><sx:sync version="1" id="VSDIO4e330eBvPCQ3Qfpug==" /></outline><outline text="This will always be true even as you travel through this lifetime and the hallways of eternity."><sx:sync version="1" id="Msm4u8nVl0mInhVCGIizXw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="CdrKXvIOzEKcydDdqrXgVg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="pHY+bKjZVUyJ4TJzCk6mKA==" /></outline><outline text="You will forget everything"><outline text="Part of the adventure of being a human is to forget who you really are. As an incarnated being, you become dominated by direct sensory awareness of the material world. Other dimensions of being are a distant memory."><sx:sync version="1" id="PNFuy4eGnE6jKAQI5+vvpg==" /></outline><outline text="This situation gives the incarnated being the creative license to create experiences that would not otherwise be possible. Anything goes."><sx:sync version="1" id="/rtKaafoFkuhsdxWEH8gQg==" /></outline><outline text="When a being is born into this world, this infant is filled with loving awareness. Gradually the child becomes immersed and identified with worldly concerns. The spiritual realities fade into the background"><sx:sync version="1" id="lPJcnF6BO0yr5FwEvV4acg==" /></outline><outline text="Each person perceives themselves as separate from others. This creates problems. It's not surprising that self-centered beings perform selfish actions."><sx:sync version="1" id="XgF/IVj6gEGrZGWtjBtMGw==" /></outline><outline text="The actions of a self-centered being tend to ignore the needs of others or even take aggressive action against others. Sooner or later, this creates suffering."><sx:sync version="1" id="4ZdZEGZwvUaXExUKXP3WFg==" /></outline><outline text="In general, most adults in western cultures are not much aware of Supreme Love and they do not take advantage of the vast spiritual resources that are available."><sx:sync version="1" id="VuJwfFCGsU+aZNtjt5oedA==" /></outline><outline text="Infinite wisdom remains dormant, waiting to emerge when requested."><sx:sync version="1" id="lk1M0qLmCk+SrfbdpKlZTA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="trDcDQjFGUGyfvVeThr5qQ==" /></outline><outline text="Your mission - Recover the missing light"><outline text="There is a light in this world that is more powerful than any darkness. This invincible light has come to earth in the form of you, and in the form of all beings and objects, both animate and inanimate."><sx:sync version="1" id="OhxHgG/gWkK3YxYHFJQv4w==" /></outline><outline text="Like a hero from an ancient myth, you're on a mission to find this treasure. You must defeat the enemies so that the kingdom can be saved. But it's really about you confronting yourself. And it's custom-made for you to fail in dealing with it. And the more you run from this confrontation, the more you run into it."><sx:sync version="1" id="CCiYilHTCEG+aKAPU8Unsw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="hOn3cuvqIEuGCV93Dopl1A==" /></outline><outline text="We tell you what to dream"><outline text="The world is rich with diverse cultures, but in one way they are all the same: each one imposes beliefs and&#xA;expects certain behaviors."><sx:sync version="1" id="6zuIXlSL5kKLdzM0pyAtcg==" /></outline><outline text="Culture is valuable for helping society to survive. It is reassuring to have concepts and beliefs to make sense of the world. But reality is more complex and nuanced than the concepts. Our belief systems are both useful and problematic."><sx:sync version="1" id="SwN/LukNA0WQFN61x7vs1w==" /></outline><outline text="From the inside, every culture appears logical and obvious. But it is valid only because the members agree on it's validity. We forget that the entire system is built on beliefs that are human inventions."><sx:sync version="1" id="QUmYIBq5OkqNUl+EbNRRew==" /></outline><outline text="There is no culture that provides the final and correct instructions for being a person. There is not even an unbiased authority that is qualified to evaluate cultural systems. Every person is a product of a particular culture, and so everyone is biased."><sx:sync version="1" id="+2NT++sZA0umj+0cUhybeQ==" /></outline><outline text="Cultural norms are passed down from generation to generation. The child absorbs information like a sponge and imitates whoever is around, mostly family members."><sx:sync version="1" id="679zrSmrzUO3o0d/LVbbaw==" /></outline><outline text="Gradually the child learns all the social and cultural conventions. Over decades, the child becomes dominated by social pressures that dictate behavior."><sx:sync version="1" id="/zZws1YvC0CcPx2k7JFt7g==" /></outline><outline text="The original joy and spontaneity of childhood gets lost along the way. The child, now grown up, thinks and lives according to external authorities, fighting battles that were set up by someone else."><sx:sync version="1" id="Kwl9Pn6FVEeGk+O8907Ifg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="C8xcfXa9sEGMCjpOvjFRPw==" /></outline><outline text="You are not the boss of me!"><outline text="Most people do not question the social boundaries of who they are and what they can be: cultural roles, expectations of family and friends, self-imposed limitations."><sx:sync version="1" id="YECm1TwQjUqhO710BncWiA==" /></outline><outline text="Spiritual freedom requires that you seize control of your life. Take responsibility for your thoughts and actions. Be impeccable with your thoughts and actions."><sx:sync version="1" id="zTtZZ+WnS0Cc3ycNTNqyXg==" /></outline><outline text="The time Don Juan challenged Carlos Casteneda"><outline text="DJ - Do you think you and I are equals?"><sx:sync version="1" id="wwQTA4r0Rkao2EkRSUagVw==" /></outline><outline text="CC - Of course, we are equals."><sx:sync version="1" id="lu6B+fQQ9U2lLfIWPUFBSA==" /></outline><outline text="DJ - No, we are not equals. I am a hunter and a warrior and you are a pimp. You are pimping for someone else."><sx:sync version="1" id="oDCNG4f3yUC9UGNm00NDPQ==" /></outline><outline text="DJ - You are not fighting your own battles but the battles of some unknown people."><sx:sync version="1" id="K6vMmEPAtUSS4tB/bzA+wg==" /></outline><outline text="- from &quot;Journey to Ixtlan&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="SxnPwXEy2Umu5l+u32htlQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="myzS5gKVAkWhW2RAmyCM3A==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="WkDZk4WYg0aZiYc6lb8BBA==" /></outline><outline text="Take control of your thoughts"><outline text="Observe and challenge your thought patterns, beliefs, and habits."><sx:sync version="1" id="Jo/Xn4tFM0+CncBkUtIx1g==" /></outline><outline text="Don't indulge in negative narratives. Focus on higher thoughts, happy thoughts, loving thoughts."><sx:sync version="1" id="xRTe4T6jeE+pgb9DTrYBDA==" /></outline><outline text="Is your behavior predictable? Are your habits helpful? What social conventions do you follow? Is your life a creative adventure?"><sx:sync version="1" id="fTVNDoGq4k+Y77A6qWoEOQ==" /></outline><outline text="Look for beliefs about personal identity. What are the dominant aspects of your self-concept? What aspects are you most proud of and attached to? What aspects of your self-concept cause suffering? "><sx:sync version="1" id="B9rAcpX2j0iFTjy5I9zalw==" /></outline><outline text="Don't get totally lost in your roles in the social drama. Remember there is a superhero inside you - a multidimensional being of light."><sx:sync version="1" id="gtPMmBjIAU2G36khrbEIBQ==" /></outline><outline text="For every belief, ask yourself, &quot;Does this belief serve me? Does it make me feel joyous?&quot; If a belief or thought pattern doesn't serve you, do the work to change it."><sx:sync version="1" id="r5Bnyd74V0aF+AsGA8Qb8w==" /></outline><outline text="Every time you notice a self-imposed limitation or other unhelpful belief, imagine that the opposite belief is true. And whatever emotions are associated with the unhelpful belief, generate the opposite emotions."><sx:sync version="1" id="vZo5A2v8aEyXtdVu5soxfA==" /></outline><outline text="Changing habitual thought patterns takes perseverance. Be patient."><sx:sync version="1" id="Wheg1s2HEEi7iyLs/rRptg==" /></outline><outline text="You may think it is impossible to change your deep beliefs about who you are. You may think there is no way to recover from the events of your personal history. In that case, your idea of what is possible is a limiting belief that does not serve you."><sx:sync version="1" id="11cIk+DZ2UubGBbzEzFxVQ==" /></outline><outline text="No matter how deeply your spirit is injured, you can be made new again."><sx:sync version="1" id="DyfLIB6ob0iJCxoAm3MubA==" /></outline><outline text="Stop with the worthless thoughts"><outline text="Don't seek prestige, status, or fame"><sx:sync version="1" id="gOjy/dlS5k6C/oHKZAPMmQ==" /></outline><outline text="Don't objectify or exploit other people"><sx:sync version="1" id="C2ufLSuBZk+SswUSqLUwwA==" /></outline><outline text="Don't be rude or aggressive"><sx:sync version="1" id="4yXY0KYlakadq1UnQtRjMg==" /></outline><outline text="Avoid dark thoughts and emotions such as frustration, dissatisfaction, stress, anxiety, anger, and compulsive behavior"><sx:sync version="1" id="2HA88RJDTEiRnfB9ZITqqg==" /></outline><outline text="Don't indulge in hatred."><sx:sync version="1" id="ZcovwH+DzECUgrPM8HVwvA==" /></outline><outline text="No self pity. No whining. No complaining."><sx:sync version="1" id="/BK1Xtts+0u1f+YYRKf7dA==" /></outline><outline text="Don't fill your mind with violent story lines or judgmental narratives from media or any other source."><sx:sync version="1" id="TDif+R4xTEWK3udGnK3etg==" /></outline><outline text="Maintain your independent psychic space especially when around negative people."><sx:sync version="1" id="uHKt3kpcJ0m0GHa/tivwdQ==" /></outline><outline text="Disassemble your mental box. Ruthlessly reject obsolete beliefs."><sx:sync version="1" id="2vJRQ+csNkqGCDeWUrWO8g==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="r7tokmpRbUqkNwTwYby+qw==" /></outline><outline text="Focus on positive thoughts"><outline text="Be compassionate and loving toward everyone."><sx:sync version="1" id="nR/hMzFwXkeLoETbYUHJrw==" /></outline><outline text="Be open to challenge and change."><sx:sync version="1" id="xh/Dy0Pv9Uq81/GhHSsvAA==" /></outline><outline text="Support universal rights and equality."><sx:sync version="1" id="jU8soZLDc0aUvfDHiC5q7A==" /></outline><outline text="Protect other people and the living world."><sx:sync version="1" id="8+tMbW/BfUiJyOXhi9dLDg==" /></outline><outline text="Think about what is more important than your own life. Serve and defend the people and everything you love."><sx:sync version="1" id="Ve0GbpLszkyFgj6haukoXg==" /></outline><outline text="Know that there is an invisible universe that is helping you and guiding you."><sx:sync version="1" id="bveff7u5F0ODcrMZaFCh9A==" /></outline><outline text="Remember that you are a powerful being of light."><sx:sync version="1" id="K9JA9NzQnUWWBgo4IlJESg==" /></outline><outline text="You can access boundless reserves of energy, love and patience."><sx:sync version="1" id="CEQgCkWgr0KLGXv9MQZ8qw==" /></outline><outline text="Move forward with confidence and enthusiasm."><sx:sync version="1" id="/O+xV9bRB0itFRVwZXwmkA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="BMsQ8cHJAk6LTB1rKwdBxA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="L5Dfj0k8y0yi3dkx5ted3Q==" /></outline><outline text="Review of the Big Picture"><outline text="For the soul that is incarnated as a human being on planet earth, it is normal to be identified with the body. Let's try to understand why this is so, and what to do about it."><sx:sync version="1" id="ygp/uC6+1EaXrgdZ4gd73w==" /></outline><outline text="The Divine Creative Force has always existed. This divinity has manifested itself in the form of this world. Everything exists inside the Creator: Planet Earth, the Universe, All-That-Is."><sx:sync version="1" id="Y5SJlKjGLkujsHo2qZFJ6g==" /></outline><outline text="More specifically, the Divine Creative Force has manifested itself in the form of all created beings. The created beings are sent out to explore every kind of experience. On this planet, it is normal for an incarnated soul to become completely identified with the body."><sx:sync version="1" id="QDIz3Qo1P06EUrLDGGNPSw==" /></outline><outline text="The body is a vehicle in which the soul can explore realities that would otherwise not be possible."><sx:sync version="1" id="c13V+Y1eB0OCLVnl8kOUAQ==" /></outline><outline text="When you understand the nature of the body and you know what is going on in the world, there is no denying that this is a very cruel way to run the universe. Full stop. "><sx:sync version="1" id="r5blvdwRb0y/GoRE3q3pUA==" /></outline><outline text="Why is there unbearable suffering in the world? As far as I know, this question has no acceptable answer."><sx:sync version="1" id="oSEhFbMt20q4eTfflwfe0Q==" /></outline><outline text="So it may happen that some essential part of yourself becomes broken, can't be fixed, is gone forever. Then what options do you have, when no band-aids will help? When no platitudes will help?"><sx:sync version="1" id="O7R20LA3ukKn1dnjdqFBBg==" /></outline><outline text="Your only viable choice is to pour your heart and soul into an all-out effort to rediscover the power and divinity that is inside you."><sx:sync version="1" id="U2sFoT5PlESOLhi3w/uKkA==" /></outline><outline text="&quot;When you search for truth, Truth itself will assist you.&quot; - Anandamayi Ma"><sx:sync version="1" id="wvuOBJXt2UCBBWTENqBzeQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="FiInf/QTl0mbBol2A/xufQ==" /></outline><outline text="Live in the moment"><outline text="Don't spend much time brooding about the past or imagining the future."><sx:sync version="1" id="QcpRhZqrskGYzmtDdZRv7A==" /></outline><outline text="Sure, we can plan for the future but live in the present. Your purpose is not to arrive at some future moment when things will be better."><sx:sync version="1" id="DrnIpM+/VUaxzGwZfJVoXA==" /></outline><outline text="Don't wait! Be fully alive now."><sx:sync version="1" id="y0uKGPiQgEO7Anv0U8NivQ==" /></outline><outline text="Notice when a conversation focuses too much on the past or future. Notice when people feel compelled to tell stories that distract too much from what is happening now. You will know when it is too much. "><sx:sync version="1" id="FTotnK7jD0Grgj2fnzpDPA==" /></outline><outline text="These conversations pull your awareness into the other person's version of reality. Avoid being pulled into unhelpful versions of reality."><sx:sync version="1" id="DLpsG5zbPkOEEjVndtBQng==" /></outline><outline text="Keep your mind clear of unnecessary thoughts. Can you stop the inner dialogue, the narratives in your mind?"><sx:sync version="1" id="kK8NMYDeJEGFeoEhA2v3CA==" /></outline><outline text="Notice the moments when you are focused on the here and now. You step into the sunlight and there is an instant of innocent joy, a moment of clear consciousness, shining in the eternal present."><sx:sync version="1" id="tDxQlqUHkEyp5ZJyocBt/Q==" /></outline><outline text="If you need more tips about living in the present, look to the world's foremost authorities on joyous living - Children!"><sx:sync version="1" id="wjkNDeQ2pkq1OlNM93qrjg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="7I+fTB2xnEu+KleSKnHNNw==" /></outline><outline text="Listen for inner guidance"><outline text="When facing any difficulty or decision, ask for help from your Inner Sources of Divine Intelligence."><sx:sync version="1" id="vH8ritODdUeTwflLuJMKHw==" /></outline><outline text="Suspend all skepticism and allow the Higher Intelligence to perform it's magic."><sx:sync version="1" id="NVhgqZDPn0KM7AsOhIBSkw==" /></outline><outline text="When you want advice or help, the first step is to quiet your mind as much as possible. Sit quietly and be vigilant to notice when the next thought emerges. Be absolutely attentive, like a cat that is staring at a mouse hole, waiting for a mouse to come out. You are watching for the next thought that arises. Catch it, but don't follow it. Let the thought go on it's way like a cloud moving across the sky. Go back to watching with full attention for the next thought."><sx:sync version="1" id="bXOVoMcVAEGM1bhW+oSCiw==" /></outline><outline text="With practice and determination, the flow of thoughts will slow down."><sx:sync version="1" id="b//DMrLvlki5o7Aya5blyg==" /></outline><outline text="When the flow of thoughts is reduced and your mind is peaceful, now you are more receptive. While maintaining this meditative state, hold your request or question in your mind. Then watch vigilantly for anything that comes back."><sx:sync version="1" id="KoJ6Ud7G+kWg7e3s+Johsw==" /></outline><outline text="Seemingly random images, memories, or emotions may emerge in your mind. Stay in the meditative state, trying to keep your mind still like a blank screen where the answer can appear. The images may make sense later."><sx:sync version="1" id="Cj0Pdcbq5Emwyerk3q9IUQ==" /></outline><outline text="Sometimes the answer becomes obvious immediately. In other cases, helpful insights may emerge later. Sometimes you will find that there was no specific answer, and yet you gain acceptance of the situation."><sx:sync version="1" id="DzGzVc4nkkW7n5bidBMXbg==" /></outline><outline text="Many questions, especially the difficult ones, don't have an answer that can be expressed in words."><sx:sync version="1" id="8fCqBRTjs0SuqgUMAWjvWg==" /></outline><outline text="Sometimes the answer will manifest as some event in your life such as a random conversation or an unexpected opportunity."><sx:sync version="1" id="h08wrNd5ikCemJkXJ4+B4w==" /></outline><outline text="Another technique is to ask for advice about your issue when you lie down to go to sleep. As you relax and wait for sleep to come, imagine you are connected to an invisible universe. Have a conversation with the stars in this invisible universe about your problem, desire, or feelings."><sx:sync version="1" id="KRD+0Cl9SEawma9MvFNLNQ==" /></outline><outline text="Your helpers will work in the background to help you with your request. Maybe not immediately, but something will manifest, something will change."><sx:sync version="1" id="XWC6+l90gEW0lQSc7h1GvQ==" /></outline><outline text="When you are inspired by inner guidance, that inner knowledge is all the permission you need to do whatever you are inspired to do. You can follow any path in life. You can do any kind of work or creative endeavor. You can be a fully spiritual being while fully engaged in the world. Regardless of the path you choose, the principles of spirituality will help you find maximum happiness."><sx:sync version="1" id="c1lHj4w6P0Cdcx2uf3n9Rg==" /></outline><outline text="Where does inner guidance come from?"><outline text="It's difficult or impossible to explain the source of inner guidance. However, we have lots of spiritual vocabulary. And many sources that are advocated as fountains of wisdom:"><sx:sync version="1" id="+X1tvq7xp0O9/8e75sgRcQ==" /></outline><outline text="- Intuition"><sx:sync version="1" id="CgN7NJeWIk6Gf5u+irWnuw==" /></outline><outline text="- Your Higher Self"><sx:sync version="1" id="GyoEVjmGUUCGBSn2H+Oy1w==" /></outline><outline text="- Universal Mind"><sx:sync version="1" id="uehtcAEUKEqRBjFAC1xwpA==" /></outline><outline text="- God's Will"><sx:sync version="1" id="D9sDgWZQ5EOVMyhUNh9LGA==" /></outline><outline text="- Spirit Helpers such as Angels, Ancestors, Animal Spirits, Mountain Spirits"><sx:sync version="1" id="OXS9XKeKzUiKEUt4KrFRuA==" /></outline><outline text="- Christ, Hanuman, Saraswati, Virgin of Guadalupe, and countless Deities of all cultures"><sx:sync version="1" id="jy0ZMa6zY0mY9f/2v5I6xA==" /></outline><outline text="- Spiritual Masters - Mata Amritanandamayi Devi, Neem Karoli Baba, Anandamayi Ma, Milarepa, St Francis"><sx:sync version="1" id="sJ7LQZoZHk66oIQbnI74bA==" /></outline><outline text="Fortunately it's not necessary to understand where Inner Wisdom comes from."><sx:sync version="1" id="cCBu6N1FV0qdyE/dm6+UQA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="VQt9V5eeRUmmOmH2JrK+Rg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="3OFxPWePZkK+bNWP7lY2sA==" /></outline><outline text="Discover catalysts for spiritual power"><outline text="Based on your unique qualities and preferences, invent new methods to awaken spiritual power. "><sx:sync version="1" id="07bLhFeZE0Gd748WgL1CCQ==" /></outline><outline text="There are no rules. Try different things until you discover your path."><sx:sync version="1" id="dozubVpPH0iSmyFswQgGtQ==" /></outline><outline text="What does spiritual power look like?"><outline text="It is difficult to generalize about the many varieties of spiritual experiences."><sx:sync version="1" id="CPjjfIM0Tkq8vPrC36ljjw==" /></outline><outline text="You may feel overwhelmed with innocent joy and happiness."><sx:sync version="1" id="pq1eEwZaLUaojsf3JHMrzg==" /></outline><outline text="You may experience pure love and tears of compassion for all beings, a love so pure that you want this moment to last forever."><sx:sync version="1" id="gjqBKuHjV0SZBt7qpowQoA==" /></outline><outline text=" You may realize that the natural world that surrounds you, the wind, the trees, the stars, and the entire living world is aware of you and is responding to you."><sx:sync version="1" id="H+NSWmxhdkqRqNYdvU4a3Q==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="sMi3Vxs8QESmSDeNLGCw8A==" /></outline><outline text="Random suggestions"><outline text="Sing gospel songs with a church or inter-faith choir."><sx:sync version="1" id="6tIlGraucUyDh919m6PWnA==" /></outline><outline text="Serve coffee and cookies to homeless people."><sx:sync version="1" id="QOzTZT+c0UihQWQ9G2m4cg==" /></outline><outline text="Stand on a rocky beach on a stormy night, absorbing power."><sx:sync version="1" id="WWf+Fvnfc06f49lLeVOrag==" /></outline><outline text="Recite Bible verses while blasting out classic rock."><sx:sync version="1" id="M1tAQUjXQ0mcTZo792R8Hg==" /></outline><outline text="Invent ceremonies to connect with the living conscious Mother Earth."><sx:sync version="1" id="MAy2t+IqKEKridbzQgzmyw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="cPRA4w/pIEaIRNA74LRp4Q==" /></outline><outline text="Meditation"><outline text="Find a type of meditation that works for you."><sx:sync version="1" id="FXaGTHk8bUK//s2sDzu5Uw==" /></outline><outline text="Meditate in a conducive location, such as a church or temple. Natural locations can be especially good, such as under a tree, on a mountain, or overlooking the ocean. A quiet room is also excellent."><sx:sync version="1" id="05NJEvJhZ0eWv16x/QoAEg==" /></outline><outline text="At first, meditation may bring forth your fears and neuroses so you can gradually overcome them."><sx:sync version="1" id="26vCcJ+uyUiEyXAjqcX/Vw==" /></outline><outline text="Daily practice is important but sometimes you won't feel like doing it. You will think it's not working. Try your best to continue."><sx:sync version="1" id="/9eRmJ/xOU2l7meKWgtQoA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="Y4sX6eHs0UGXXGaVwPfGWg==" /></outline><outline text="Silence"><outline text="Keep silent for a day."><sx:sync version="1" id="JuF/RY1ZYU6uwL/P18Q/5w==" /></outline><outline text="Observe how this effects your mood and vibration."><sx:sync version="1" id="qnxTiSHCpk2Q/snj0NPtrQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="/mBHsO5la0e7j12lMX7kxA==" /></outline><outline text="Grounding"><outline text="Take a comfortable position in a peaceful place. Imagine there is a strong channel of energy, your grounding cord, that goes from the base of your spine to the center of the earth."><sx:sync version="1" id="aYYqE1oKtkmLQNnl8muzgA==" /></outline><outline text="With each breath, imagine all negative emotions and unwanted thoughts are flowing down your grounding cord and being absorbed and neutralized by Mother Earth."><sx:sync version="1" id="bNAQc9XWoEWAx+STGerREQ==" /></outline><outline text="At the same time, with each breath, imagine healing earth energy is coming up through your feet and the base of your spine."><sx:sync version="1" id="V6AuX5P0UEuFZ1Hrl6s3DQ==" /></outline><outline text="Breathe deeply, being aware of every inhalation and exhalation. Be aware of energy moving in both directions. Observe the color of the energy. Increase the vibration. Ask for more. Be very determined and insistent. "><sx:sync version="1" id="MMdD/eD1RE+UpvzsYT+myQ==" /></outline><outline text="Continue until you feel completely clear and energized."><sx:sync version="1" id="Jd9n4XicekapwGX8NPTFTw==" /></outline><outline text="With practice, you will feel grounded all the time."><sx:sync version="1" id="pIG+KxK4+k6dCCTm5RLVxw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="Ya3kCdUUpUy7oqoqWHMpTg==" /></outline><outline text="Best catalyst"><outline text="Spend time with a God-realized person"><sx:sync version="1" id="f2H218mJR0agioJwU/M1ag==" /></outline><outline text="If you are so fortunate to find such a being, their radiant presence will transform you, and awaken the spiritual power within you."><sx:sync version="1" id="HxlRLkhtrkafrpsoCL7oaQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="uqysgD4Egk2oKuaYE0gBJg==" /></outline><outline text="Divine Grace"><outline text="You can think of these suggested catalysts as ways of invoking Divine Grace."><sx:sync version="1" id="Y9ut/nAaDE6lvUaqf+/c/w==" /></outline><outline text="Personal effort is under our control. Divine Grace, not so much."><sx:sync version="1" id="LcspksdZAkC3Gcc4Xcqdeg==" /></outline><outline text="Divine Grace usually comes when you least expect it."><sx:sync version="1" id="x9IWfBWaekWLjyd9CX+ujw==" /></outline><outline text="When you understand, even for a moment, that everything is perfect as is, that understanding is a gift of Divine Grace."><sx:sync version="1" id="mGnheo5+P0qFObu7TckBAg==" /></outline><outline text="When you love the Supreme Creator with all your heart, that is a gift of Divine Grace."><sx:sync version="1" id="19bcxsgLnEqqMTLuzolgVg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="6ChzGkUqyEGPXI1xNLc5Tw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="Prv3NykyjE2iAFwEU6wcRQ==" /></outline><outline text="Be impeccable with your speech"><outline text="Words are powerful"><outline text="Spoken words are a form of manifestation and wield immense power."><sx:sync version="1" id="88OPIZiOkkSYcvLdz8FyCg==" /></outline><outline text="The spoken word is one of the primary ways we create our reality."><sx:sync version="1" id="WDpanx2A5EyrJJZeulua4g==" /></outline><outline text="The words that you speak contribute to the vibration of the world."><sx:sync version="1" id="Vy2FlKEOEEeGTeIH+UWz0Q==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="Z+7yct5fcke287aK48fOAA==" /></outline><outline text="Tell the truth"><outline text="Always tell the truth and be kind."><sx:sync version="1" id="031N1VBwsECuciZ9PTtkkA==" /></outline><outline text="If the truth seems unkind, you have to find a way to express the truth with kindness."><sx:sync version="1" id="reIpHNGqnEuXotN7G2KyKQ==" /></outline><outline text="Resist the temptation to bend the truth to protect your reputation or self-image. Go with full transparency."><sx:sync version="1" id="0yctW0frukWcFZIHlo+tDg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="NCg5rQQYxkiw67yqPUHjlg==" /></outline><outline text="Respect for all"><outline text="Your speech should always show respect for every person and every being, always."><sx:sync version="1" id="/S9JPo7+8UWULFgWTzlKlg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="UhAqonO6+EOUPpFh60FiVQ==" /></outline><outline text="No whining"><outline text="Don't complain about things that are unimportant"><sx:sync version="1" id="iy91J4N0EEqn7b+6zFCX2A==" /></outline><outline text="For important things, also don't complain."><sx:sync version="1" id="I3zim0eeSEOR2DWTjcEt9A==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="eMW7+6IKLkOSEqzx/yXgAA==" /></outline><outline text="No preaching. Don't give advice."><outline text="For those who ask for advice, encourage them to find their own answer."><sx:sync version="1" id="gRF/3AfNYUKwKRJWdzM8FA==" /></outline><outline text="For those in crisis, you can walk them through the basic spiritual principles."><sx:sync version="1" id="kXgk5ejUeUCo8pGe4L/swQ==" /></outline><outline text="Beware of unhealthy dependency."><sx:sync version="1" id="sphmqZV3ZkSyHu13Q7tm9Q==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="YMLtQIGYd0CAx0+b7IDTGg==" /></outline><outline text="No gossip"><outline text="Gossip is like a toxic spill in the group mind."><sx:sync version="1" id="wQEtALBDC0WHRriTUAfO8w==" /></outline><outline text="As much as possible, avoid speaking about people who are not present."><sx:sync version="1" id="uxGsemZjjE+CITYjmKUpRg==" /></outline><outline text="Find a way to leave the conversation."><sx:sync version="1" id="m8Za0gXry0evQgA6BdYPzA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="4I46DochUkS6zwj7FhsswA==" /></outline><outline text="Impulsive talking"><outline text="Control the impulse to share your opinion"><outline text="- The clue is when you want to interrupt someone."><sx:sync version="1" id="mfDEcxcQt0eOL/2TCT3IuA==" /></outline><outline text="- If your opinion is needed and relevant, and there is a least some receptivity, fine, go ahead."><sx:sync version="1" id="5zAbqqkN30ahNEukdCljzA==" /></outline><outline text="- More often, no one wants or needs your opinion."><sx:sync version="1" id="Hnd2P7takUKpuu3aSSwpAA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="3QM1jFR8m0CioOT3PA5Apg==" /></outline><outline text="Control the impulse to share personal history or your inner world. "><outline text="What are the stories that you always tell?"><sx:sync version="1" id="EsHp7qkzkEm1MpkKgJULmw==" /></outline><outline text="What are the habitual ways you explain your personal history?"><sx:sync version="1" id="Ot+g6Yy3O0OYPV66iW8LmA==" /></outline><outline text="Stop reinforcing this facade and fabricated identity."><sx:sync version="1" id="uXHF4k3oTkaPjhnWw+nTlA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="cYkIIL+BfUalV8SF3rwYow==" /></outline><outline text="These impulses typically lead to unnecessary conversations, further distractions, and an overall loss of spiritual energy."><sx:sync version="1" id="XVWdamBNVUqIm8tdz5oo7A==" /></outline><outline text="There is a sense of self-importance that drives these impulses. You want to eliminate this sense of self-importance."><sx:sync version="1" id="sIMl/7iOkkqouLjOpM3ufw==" /></outline><outline text="Maintaining inner silence is usually better than random conversations."><sx:sync version="1" id="frih2zPsTEyH3+V+l1lviQ==" /></outline><outline text="At times, you may want to share experiences with allies on the spiritual path"><outline text="Don't over do it."><sx:sync version="1" id="kS5gnbnFREqiWym9rpjBeg==" /></outline><outline text="Ask yourself, &quot;Am I bragging or complaining? Am I building up my ego? Is this helpful?&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="0penT3kpEUCqPbA4NWlMZA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="Ae666seJyk6SS+wJWR8x6Q==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="HXVgGR5xaU6YpyHAjap/vQ==" /></outline><outline text="You will be tested"><outline text="Your ability to be impeccable with your speech will be tested by encounters in the world."><sx:sync version="1" id="vDiRfnT4w0Ocd6wfoww88Q==" /></outline><outline text="Don't worry. We will go over strategies for how to react (or not react) to these encounters."><sx:sync version="1" id="v7OVN32jV0mZrg6XFlxHvA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="ArOO7cOLbESJqqId2Gi+0w==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="ft3b6j9T2EWRtI084wPs4Q==" /></outline><outline text="Equanimity vs Everyone"><outline text="Starting point"><outline text="Know yourself to be an innocent child of the universe, who is loved and cherished."><sx:sync version="1" id="2xXWozxoQkCOOOzpDR9SOA==" /></outline><outline text="Experience the serene and loving vibration that comes with this knowledge."><sx:sync version="1" id="bkENViY7qkSf0GhZuXPzdw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="9tdHVBCqE0alKZmbI19H2Q==" /></outline><outline text="The Burn"><outline text="After experiencing this Divine Vibration, you may experience a burning desire to stay in this vibration always. "><sx:sync version="1" id="JmqkusqTxkW+YvMQPgxE3g==" /></outline><outline text="This is the best thing that can happen to you."><sx:sync version="1" id="43eu8x91g0K72yJpJveE1w==" /></outline><outline text="Focus completely on this burning desire. Feel it breaking open your heart. Think about it day and night. Be obsessed."><sx:sync version="1" id="lK8lcvTlm0C7Hq9IiTNhlw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="/IBXINgpV0KCBHZHDiwoKA==" /></outline><outline text="Protect the flame"><outline text="Despite your best intentions, your vibration will occasionally be disrupted during daily life, especially during emotional interactions."><sx:sync version="1" id="V0nUaOHGlUmrv2SfRt0jng==" /></outline><outline text="Like a seed that is germinating, a spiritual seeker needs to protect the Divine Vibration from disruption."><sx:sync version="1" id="Vqu7bVMoIkePFaKncIShTQ==" /></outline><outline text="Do your best to maintain the Divine Vibration as you fulfill your daily responsibilities."><sx:sync version="1" id="RuA7NOPlR0iwMDJrN1pXpw==" /></outline><outline text="Do everything you can to avoid negativity. "><sx:sync version="1" id="P3dTUMa/vkO2nOp/cPTefw==" /></outline><outline text="Gradually, the spiritual seeker merges into the Divine Vibration."><sx:sync version="1" id="IK4RjVRNPEOILy4Tv7bdDw==" /></outline><outline text="As strength and equanimity increase, the Divine Vibration burns brighter. You become a flame that can light other lamps."><sx:sync version="1" id="+KduZqqx9EavBDasbRaxPA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="6YK886hycEONqw7HD/BW+g==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="07EcOEMKq0yPz/QdI0mO3w==" /></outline><outline text="Remain mysterious and unknown"><outline text="The role of support networks"><outline text="Most people find great enjoyment in their social networks of family and friends. That is the reality they love."><sx:sync version="1" id="bSZ14SyKgUKpbC4emjsvmg==" /></outline><outline text="They depend on their interactions with other people for their emotional well-being and to validate their experiences."><sx:sync version="1" id="r6BgvwPmckyVX1FhWw0pBw==" /></outline><outline text="Social interactions are powerful constructs that keep one locked in a rigid identity. This can be comfortable. Until it's not."><sx:sync version="1" id="Mvex7SH7d0WYFWK2m6W0rg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="ncBPHyomHkGSARSOa2843A==" /></outline><outline text="There is another path for those who want to dissolve their ties to the world."><sx:sync version="1" id="ntho7yvbR0aMj+Ua8z+Ajg==" /></outline><outline text="Disclaimer about Becoming Unknown"><outline text="This path is for:"><outline text="- those with a sincere desire for inner freedom"><sx:sync version="1" id="O/R/2f9ZEEeDbUKmU6bDMg==" /></outline><outline text="- those who don't want the entanglements and illusions of worldly life"><sx:sync version="1" id="QkklKBQms0C2O8BiUYexQw==" /></outline><outline text="- those who don't need anything from anybody"><sx:sync version="1" id="n8aDtrQ8CU6JeV803o2XMA==" /></outline><outline text="- those who have abandoned social norms"><sx:sync version="1" id="/LCWsvz/dkOjI7UaVe9Svg==" /></outline><outline text="- who care nothing about recognition"><sx:sync version="1" id="Ot3H5I20BkuTs3LwOPikaQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="Tc1NUj6RbEqflPNZTBpUTw==" /></outline><outline text="This path is NOT for:"><outline text="- avoiding unresolved emotional wounds"><sx:sync version="1" id="csIp53wDwkW2UkVR/r/STg==" /></outline><outline text="- recovering from social anxiety or depression"><sx:sync version="1" id="MSOhZkhz20GG0W8JNqT9mQ==" /></outline><outline text="- avoiding karmic responsibilities such as children"><sx:sync version="1" id="AvXhJ3njMEO7HSGDOdpa1A==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="qYIg27U2TUmsg9v67ZOsMw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="RHd4PhINGUmLLFTAuTGVEQ==" /></outline><outline text="People like to put you in a box"><outline text="We know that our family members and others ask questions so they can make comparisons and judgements."><sx:sync version="1" id="o77BpTdhlUqyBC9MVpOwgw==" /></outline><outline text="They create narratives about you and put you in a box. Their thoughts attempt to pin you down. It's just what people do."><sx:sync version="1" id="/p1dsGjTL06B621APcnxLg==" /></outline><outline text="It seems that these thoughts and narratives about you create psychic strings that are attached to you. Remember, all of us are connected in the Universal Mind."><sx:sync version="1" id="RNGF5p36UUKB8YnzpWIPZA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="ntGQVUn0skGIDnl6L4lxUA==" /></outline><outline text="Gradually dissolve the box"><outline text="How is it possible to become disentangled from people's thoughts, and allow the box to dissolve, the box that people see you in?"><sx:sync version="1" id="dmJCKkbPeUCN9WtmO715sw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="g4gRmKOyXUeuRLq7pqLjZw==" /></outline><outline text="Create a fog around yourself"><outline text="Only explain the minimum about yourself, preferably nothing."><sx:sync version="1" id="Gs3NGXYhI0qd6X69lAa7lw==" /></outline><outline text="Maintain a distance. Remain mysterious."><sx:sync version="1" id="X4woU26dRk6xSMC8UMOxtw==" /></outline><outline text="Gradually fade into the unknown."><sx:sync version="1" id="zec9o0QyNUC/yS3T/ZhwUw==" /></outline><outline text="Stop communicating with all the people who know you well"><outline text="See the disclaimer near the beginning of this section."><sx:sync version="1" id="2VNdfrTBPUuYJlmGZvgvBQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="imsD3IitqkGdvkEAQRK52Q==" /></outline><outline text="Stop giving them information so that they can't create or update your box."><sx:sync version="1" id="1jXYgSWQaU2v4XRw1ObvPg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="qJDuRlqvIEeqcGU3/pzv8Q==" /></outline><outline text="Don't tell anyone what you are up to"><outline text="If they know you are trying to escape the box, then they assign you to the box of &quot;People who want to escape the box&quot;."><sx:sync version="1" id="Be+p3/bXGU+ejqjvLT0eTA==" /></outline><outline text="That becomes another identity that needs to be dissolved."><sx:sync version="1" id="n14AVhI8M0qAzt1WIcRPNg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="oOLrSPburkiCEHfyWGG2tA==" /></outline><outline text="You want all concepts involving you to gradually fade away without anyone noticing."><sx:sync version="1" id="3FN+Y/Q5L0SV1pAh51x1Cg==" /></outline><outline text="This is one step in merging into the Infinite"><outline text="You become like the great Tibetan Master, Milarepa -"><sx:sync version="1" id="mKRIJK0OrUmEDPyao8ElmQ==" /></outline><outline text="&quot;I have no attachment to this life.&#xA;I roam like a lion, free and alone,&#xA;in the vast expanse of sky-like mind.”"><sx:sync version="1" id="z2ZcFCYQtkGP3EPWbHgQ5Q==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="GjonrJVvhUicneRAAP/UTg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="prQQoEwarkSzM+aUa4gqOA==" /></outline><outline text="Protect Your Space"><outline text="Defend against Anger"><outline text="Do not respond to anger with more anger"><outline text="Don't feed the cycle of destructive words and behavior."><sx:sync version="1" id="alBt6+d+40KMPmjTxZd4MQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="K8t2pk1blkeBa3N/3QIgTA==" /></outline><outline text="Effects of anger and violence"><outline text="It damages the mental atmosphere of yourself and the world."><sx:sync version="1" id="04LCzSR6pU2zCoUKIKRvoQ==" /></outline><outline text="It damages both the attacked and the attacker, like a sword that is sharp on both ends."><sx:sync version="1" id="pqXwX15rlE656n0zREFPYQ==" /></outline><outline text="It creates misery."><sx:sync version="1" id="aLW0YiElDkaB0QEHhmsLqA==" /></outline><outline text="It distorts your perception."><sx:sync version="1" id="cz7a30HJRkG5aKJoAZnxEw==" /></outline><outline text="It's not effective for dealing with difficult people."><sx:sync version="1" id="1n9ghWJKv0m3jZLp5FfKyw==" /></outline><outline text="It has no benefits."><sx:sync version="1" id="w2jQQ4/b7Ua2IB4CR4Vg8A==" /></outline><outline text="It may be necessary to make a show of anger, pretending to be angry, such as when scaring cows out of the garden. But do it in a way that doesn't effect your inner peace. Never throw anyone out of your heart, ever."><sx:sync version="1" id="dTsx/Mb6yk2br92zXfJdfg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="YicPIBNv3kW7hLsaGkf4EA==" /></outline><outline text="Make a resolution to avoid expressing anger"><outline text="When negative emotions start to overpower you, let go as quickly as possible."><sx:sync version="1" id="J/QhxqwDnU+oWp0CgZPyiw==" /></outline><outline text="Tell yourself to relax. Breathe. Take a break."><sx:sync version="1" id="m8o3jtxmS0eNnFy0yNozPw==" /></outline><outline text="Generate loving thoughts."><sx:sync version="1" id="AqlndfqDg0qjO3A95AOneA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="HGu1YQ5SGUarOFsimfKEzw==" /></outline><outline text="Choose love"><outline text="When you encounter an angry person, remember this is a child of God who is doing the best they can."><sx:sync version="1" id="DNCXT2P8jEW1mtsXEcBH0A==" /></outline><outline text="Regardless of the situation, you are responsible for your inner state. You can choose love.."><sx:sync version="1" id="BIsEkVpaGEGhO33iEUwxTQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="p4qTqT51VkmwOAoV7Vymeg==" /></outline><outline text="Silence - the preferred option"><outline text="Very often the best response is silence, loving silence, compassionate silence."><sx:sync version="1" id="h1ZyXPLyx0yd8SdF74ejwg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="C0LGqAh0dEu7W5k6Szrhog==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="tawX7OxwPEK7RNtcCxYOxw==" /></outline><outline text="Defend against Hate and Racism"><outline text="This is like a surprise mid-term exam for a spiritual warrior."><sx:sync version="1" id="P0HSRvKW0kCOxnd56TGCBg==" /></outline><outline text="Clearly express why you disagree. Do not be angry or aggressive. Just tell the truth. &quot;Please don't talk about my friends that way.&quot; &quot;That's not okay with me.&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="gdK/UGU/DkmnnPvFwMCDng==" /></outline><outline text="No matter how skillful you are, the situation may escalate"><outline text="Sometimes anything you say will escalate the situation."><sx:sync version="1" id="Gq39Fct4wEm0EAxfmCmyiA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="bZC72iJyAE+Uro31sF+a3g==" /></outline><outline text="Remain as a witness. Stay with your highest thoughts."><outline text="Your non-reaction is the most powerful and defiant statement you can make."><sx:sync version="1" id="j5cRjXPDyUWx5ceZ2/RiaQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="7PwnkDcK6k6e/bETVFVH2A==" /></outline><outline text="It may be necessary to make a statement about your values."><outline text="&quot;I believe all people deserve respect, all the time.&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="kzphCeFsLkOTaKLg59uaXA==" /></outline><outline text="Then silence again."><sx:sync version="1" id="aWRK5jZeu0e0R7oheXRqyQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="cEne0tOfZ0aWNKuMHgkAQw==" /></outline><outline text="It's best to leave the area after giving an unequivocal response."><sx:sync version="1" id="NOs7J5sQW0O8M/1HWr5+XQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="o+7hko8xbESksiIxe6LOcA==" /></outline><outline text="Defend against Arguments"><outline text="Don't be drawn into arguments."><sx:sync version="1" id="CJSRtYcEiUqPpQF9Eo/hPQ==" /></outline><outline text="An argument is a confrontational exchange in which a person tries to convince another person that their own position is correct."><sx:sync version="1" id="55Cg7LBBMEyDkJeCwV8w+w==" /></outline><outline text="Instead of argument, you want dialogue."><sx:sync version="1" id="SZVCiwGndEOnzzLLB9Nx9w==" /></outline><outline text="Dialogue is a conversation where people aim to understand each other's perspectives and viewpoints."><sx:sync version="1" id="RXW4qpLlAUG8NgRMhYm58A==" /></outline><outline text="Principles for dialogue"><outline text="Maintain trust and mutual respect"><outline text="Do your best to maintain a positive relationship with everyone. Read the room."><sx:sync version="1" id="qXBYAq7Mfk2P6alDrzoJUg==" /></outline><outline text="Recognize and control the strong impulse to win the argument."><sx:sync version="1" id="COedbpdVcUKRG0Db4QnqZg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="/hpwOSm520GgnODa/yzVPg==" /></outline><outline text="Inside yourself, make an honest assessment of your role"><outline text="Did your actions or inactions cause or contribute to the problem?"><sx:sync version="1" id="r7IoT1DkFEKPcmTqjelhGw==" /></outline><outline text="Did you miss the early warning signs?"><sx:sync version="1" id="xLItW43SEUSvt3ow5/n0GA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="khbKk1GyfUCP0VW3x6qkwQ==" /></outline><outline text="Admit any mistakes or shortcomings."><sx:sync version="1" id="SMVUEkVraEai/wBpVGW76g==" /></outline><outline text="Distinguish between factual and emotional components of a situation"><outline text="Facts, the issue we are dealing with, such as:"><outline text="&quot;You spent too much money.&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="KyqfD+kdRE6zFlqNlQ5guw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="6VQKW8deU0OEo8ZyVIud+w==" /></outline><outline text="Emotional component, often implied, such as:"><outline text="&quot;I don't trust you any more.&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="2FZfFGVqJkqGmsupJ3MHdw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="is6gZ84vg061yPzK/Sicow==" /></outline><outline text="Both aspects need to be addressed, not just one, both. The spending habits need to be discussed."><sx:sync version="1" id="TbWcaq4jMUagbW1auXAbRA==" /></outline><outline text="But the conversation about spending habits is not going to very well when there are unresolved emotional issues."><sx:sync version="1" id="nixpb/tAYUeyAP5gr1LWuw==" /></outline><outline text="So the first priority is to get back to common goals and mutual respect"><sx:sync version="1" id="Ks140sitsUGRSqgC5oia0A==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="qD9Osq6D60uKn5WtoA0oFw==" /></outline><outline text="Express your emotions without blame"><outline text="&quot;When [ specific event ] happened, I felt [ specific emotion ].&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="XHyV0Kg5xUegIjYJO9yCTg==" /></outline><outline text="Avoid blaming anyone for your feelings."><sx:sync version="1" id="6bzUh9wUREGYEAFyr14/dg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="NH47T5LO5EOb1vs6gB3HUg==" /></outline><outline text="Never buy into anyone's attempt to put you down"><outline text="Your value as a child of God is never in question."><sx:sync version="1" id="5JhuILyr3UGh1Mww76ZZnQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="DBT4gdyGN06rcM6/D12K+w==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="5zKDPIMvA0qpOonXJt8iXg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="mOfTaQ7zWUusskBLyKEmbw==" /></outline><outline text="Defend against Negative Comments"><outline text="First main goal - Maintain a positive relationship with everyone."><sx:sync version="1" id="gkBk0kQWg0Ke50cHVkOjyw==" /></outline><outline text="Next main goal - Don't engage in unproductive or negative conversations."><sx:sync version="1" id="9fjZtQZMl0uhXelVsIsEEQ==" /></outline><outline text="First consider if you can simply remain silent"><outline text="Silence is very effective in many situations."><sx:sync version="1" id="Q5sypmJVbEqWwGPr0VYWNg==" /></outline><outline text="Sometimes being silent is rude and will damage your relationship with the other person."><sx:sync version="1" id="sOYOjauZUUKn5sTyxYokiA==" /></outline><outline text=" Sometimes being silent will damage third parties. For example, you should not remain silent when a hateful comment is made about anyone."><sx:sync version="1" id="Ie4RHXK0mkmS19Xnh1MfhQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="7UVo/XoOlEymhu+RMqhb4Q==" /></outline><outline text="If a verbal response is needed:"><outline text="Avoid expressing agreement with the statement because that will encourage them to continue."><sx:sync version="1" id="DfWoygtgr069WyjkALYk2A==" /></outline><outline text="In most cases, don't express disagreement with the statement because then they will try to convince you. It will escalate the situation."><sx:sync version="1" id="JDktaouER0m+1X7wPWHXfg==" /></outline><outline text="Here are some examples of non-committal responses that neither agree nor disagree:"><sx:sync version="1" id="zTcP753PHk+nVaaqJ9K13g==" /></outline><outline text="&quot;Is that right?"><sx:sync version="1" id="cA91pkpTfUeGILy/ZiBa1g==" /></outline><outline text="&quot;Oh, I see.&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="8MnZEsZ420SqEb8wRvuBAg==" /></outline><outline text="&quot;I don't know about that.&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="/8G7MD8ZFECzYmopvMP1iQ==" /></outline><outline text="&quot;I'll have to think about that.&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="jD9IfF2Fk0egP/+zGuGk3w==" /></outline><outline text="&quot;That’s a new perspective for me.&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="nseib8p56UqC8chvIkb/wg==" /></outline><outline text="&quot;I hear you.&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="szyIuboB/0OObkcKCdxCGA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="Y+9SKLeFGk2RDB54w7r8QQ==" /></outline><outline text="Keep your heart open without giving validation to any negative attitude."><sx:sync version="1" id="DfKjCJ36uUux47p7jFUj2A==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="ibXZTlzbsUKXxn86QosFsw==" /></outline><outline text="Defend against Labels and Limitations"><outline text="Don't buy into story lines about who you are. If someone verbally attacks you, don't give importance to their words."><sx:sync version="1" id="ELo2EdESTUu6K5zdNkRVlw==" /></outline><outline text="If someone vaguely implies that you are incompetent or unattractive, remember who you are, and where you come from. &quot;I am an innocent child of the universe.&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="oRvKBE0C+UWXNQzFGWtfLQ==" /></outline><outline text="When someone makes up a story about you, it is about them, their cultural biases and ego games. It is not about you. You are not responsible for their reality."><sx:sync version="1" id="qWFjw8Q68Uig94TCoL3BgA==" /></outline><outline text="Remain alert for comments that limit or define you. Someone may assign a label to you, it could be a flattering label. Through humility, you will recognize that a flattering label is just a label. You are a being of light, and you are way more amazing than any label."><sx:sync version="1" id="UNu7HHsPJ0OBz17BoV9MvQ==" /></outline><outline text="Whatever someone may say about you, the opposite is also part of who you are. All good and bad qualities, from altruism to cruelty, are present in you and every person, which means you are not better or worse than anyone else."><sx:sync version="1" id="FzD8ysJ2c0yxtNpqOJqaXQ==" /></outline><outline text="&quot;The mind is a puzzle containing truth and untruth, gods and demons, good and bad, all mixed together.&quot; - Mata Amritanandamayi"><sx:sync version="1" id="fagzOVqtEk2V+z2DltS3ug==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="lp+eCb+IkE6Qq8Z5BSqGpw==" /></outline><outline text="Defend against Emotional Manipulation"><outline text="Human beings are skillful in manipulating the emotions and behavior of others. It happens all the time."><sx:sync version="1" id="2Gyc/TglA0GTmtYVn3FXSw==" /></outline><outline text="For example an emotional charge may be conveyed indirectly through words that are not overtly harmful or manipulative. Such attacks may be subconscious, meaning the attacker is not aware of being manipulative."><sx:sync version="1" id="h9yL2lFvPUqhLElQje6VAg==" /></outline><outline text="These stealth attacks may seem insignificant and harmless. But they may work in the background to drain your energy and distract you from your natural state of happiness. The only signal may be a slight feeling of irritation, a visceral tingling, or a twinge of emotion, triggered by a comment that seems almost normal."><sx:sync version="1" id="vSeNreZ8VkGy7YhzfFMjYw==" /></outline><outline text="If your mind is already engaged in a barrage of thoughts, the additional irritation may go unnoticed. That's why a pure and quiet mind is a good defense. A pure mind is more sensitive to negativity."><sx:sync version="1" id="4VM7TpZJeEifVBmL/g43qQ==" /></outline><outline text="When you detect uncomfortable feelings, don't react immediately. You may be tempted to respond in kind,  with slightly negative comment, a passive aggressive attack. Then the person may say, as if they are innocent, &quot;What's your problem?&quot; And bam! they score an emotional hit. They make you feel inferior. This is the skillful emotional manipulation that you don't want."><sx:sync version="1" id="gqzCd640mEiCmrBnjB8Igw==" /></outline><outline text="Understand that negative and manipulative people are like a tar ball and you should take precautions to stay free of tar."><sx:sync version="1" id="/o4iRC0PLE+NxZXZuzvdXQ==" /></outline><outline text="What to do when you detect emotional manipulation"><outline text="Imagine that your aura is surrounded and protected by a boundary of roses, gorgeous and energized roses that can absorb any amount of negativity."><sx:sync version="1" id="4oHYNGsQMUmmFbSL7TJ1nQ==" /></outline><outline text="Also return to your highest thoughts. You are God's innocent child. Remember the innocent love of a child."><sx:sync version="1" id="MQIyQsCnbUi5Ohzx9kRWRA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="FpxJCHhK0kSqr707KKYbAw==" /></outline><outline text="Sometimes you may fail"><outline text="When caught off guard, you may let a mean remark slip out, leading to a painful interaction."><sx:sync version="1" id="MvqHZlTEg0qpIeCEE87gyg==" /></outline><outline text="It happens. Don't worry. You will get stronger with practice."><sx:sync version="1" id="5tv8DAP+uk2wRGmxc7wbzA==" /></outline><outline text="Eventually you will come to relish these challenges."><sx:sync version="1" id="a4LF1t0VRka1xv3PMnZTAA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="ctmRm0zqQ06u/+8IGdqAXA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="nZMzlt5jWUaFaZb5GTJr+w==" /></outline><outline text="Defend against Shadow Forces"><outline text="You may encounter negative thoughts and impulses that come from covert &quot;shadow&quot; forces that oppose spiritual development."><sx:sync version="1" id="3jexuae85Eim1r0bUhFvRQ==" /></outline><outline text="Some sources say there are forces in this world that intend for us to suffer. They say negative tendencies in the human psyche have developed into parasitic shadows that sabotage those on the spiritual path."><sx:sync version="1" id="wwdw+EDBWE+u5IHL/N4JDg==" /></outline><outline text="As you gain inner strength and purity, you may encounter obstructions that seem deliberate."><sx:sync version="1" id="cMagXHYToUyZj4sGxWXDpg==" /></outline><outline text="I admit this sounds implausible and paranoid"><outline text="As with all the claims in this document, only you can determine if this is true and relevant for you."><sx:sync version="1" id="14f4uoSI9UOFkQoNJCxkMQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="tp5/W8CJw0eLRpRfKuklng==" /></outline><outline text="Defeat shadow forces"><outline text="When you feel negative thoughts coming out of nowhere, defend yourself. "><sx:sync version="1" id="C0C8BiLo5UCkqkAOxQceew==" /></outline><outline text="Confront the thoughts, &quot;What are you doing here? Who let you in? Go away! I don't need you depleting my energy.&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="pj4oDyxs/UaEz0IRZ0gGWA==" /></outline><outline text="Surround yourself with pure white light, the Light more powerful than any darkness."><sx:sync version="1" id="5CX1Ndu/DU6I/UMyo5EbJQ==" /></outline><outline text="Call out to your Spirit Helpers for protection."><sx:sync version="1" id="PWC0Vkp3xU+U4+6CXHLkjA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="9luqfKdf+kKNQi/vocgCbg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="Y3ennh9C3ki7622DGDGVZw==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="MErcxkTsKkyY14rLL+jBMA==" /></outline><outline text="Let go of self-importance / Be humble"><outline text="The world doesn't exist to conform to your preferences. Don't be annoyed or offended by things."><sx:sync version="1" id="KY0uIwSeTkGDDckwld0RRg==" /></outline><outline text="Remember the ancient Zen teaching, &quot;The Great Way is not difficult for those who have no preferences&quot;."><sx:sync version="1" id="OkM6Km/oikSI1pjlyA5Y2g==" /></outline><outline text="Be a witness to whatever is happening without judgment."><sx:sync version="1" id="3X+bVm7RT0esfOy5KGJGHQ==" /></outline><outline text="Humility means accepting your role on this earth, and playing your part impeccably. Always do your best."><sx:sync version="1" id="Z+hMjnc2gkKLc9wM5Eg4vQ==" /></outline><outline text="Humility doesn't mean lack of self-esteem. Know that you are a good person, an awesome person. Also know you are not better than anyone else."><sx:sync version="1" id="v2JkdxsEmUOMad8gQFulDQ==" /></outline><outline text="When you are tempted to judge someone, look for their good qualities. Expand your heart with love for this person. Try to help the person to be happy and successful."><sx:sync version="1" id="yTFOT01AnEeRrDWADLyGcA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="I1r9AHKO7kmlLwH7HUtG2g==" /></outline><outline text="It's all temporary"><outline text="You are only in this body in this world for a short time."><sx:sync version="1" id="gelScyXUtE+nmNF+g2L0Tw==" /></outline><outline text="Your worldly situation can never be made secure. It appears that you can find lasting happiness when your material situation is fixed. That is not going to happen."><sx:sync version="1" id="WZURqmceIU+F9zBJEpnSvQ==" /></outline><outline text="Attempts to protect your body may be successful for some time. But no one can avoid the inevitable course of events. The body is temporary. After some time, you will discard it like a set of old clothes."><sx:sync version="1" id="cDqc6r0uv02fk/EP8DxvFA==" /></outline><outline text="There is nothing in this world that we can truly call our own. Everything belongs to God only. We come with nothing and we leave with nothing. This life will be over in a short time."><sx:sync version="1" id="htzq+X8bVUiOqx/+PpaAiQ==" /></outline><outline text="At any moment, you may cross the threshold of death."><sx:sync version="1" id="1IU8hVGFO0iE//ggQFijgA==" /></outline><outline text="Death can be exhilarating, like diving into a pool. Death is completely safe. When this life is ends, a new journey begins. "><sx:sync version="1" id="S2LV9D/dbEi5B/hmITuUMA==" /></outline><outline text="The pure consciousness that is you, is indestructible. You have always existed. You are not going anywhere. There is nowhere to go."><sx:sync version="1" id="mqpF5d9d/Ua3A1KFY/WJqw==" /></outline><outline text="But for now, we live in a material world, where we struggle to stay alive. We live in a world where good and evil are slugging it out.  "><sx:sync version="1" id="Fv0ChBL3xEGT6317EzT+4A==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="nWf9kwWTYEmlZNNmRuy0YQ==" /></outline><outline text="Do good actions"><outline text="When the opportunity arises to perform some good action, be the first to jump in and do it. Perform as many good actions as possible. Accept with joy and enthusiasm the work that comes to you. Leave the world in better condition than you found it."><sx:sync version="1" id="ZRl1tnZ680WtY7avIo34jQ==" /></outline><outline text="Don't think your work is more important than being kind. Respond compassionately to everyone in the moment. Let go of irritation and judgment."><sx:sync version="1" id="8TefKuZyDkme+kfAkPWaAw==" /></outline><outline text="If someone wants to help you with some task, let them join in, even if it takes twice as long."><sx:sync version="1" id="4AFQ/oMLTEyqRhPgSXtH2g==" /></outline><outline text="Sometimes you need to move fast, but don't be tense. Don't be rude. Make a decision to enjoy the fast pace."><sx:sync version="1" id="zd4o41y0w0+Iv/w6pIp1+A==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="R2VNUNvZPke/WQ3eeEGEhw==" /></outline><outline text="Do your best"><outline text="Whatever actions you perform, always give your best. Then you will have no regrets, regardless of the results. "><sx:sync version="1" id="no4asR31EkCffuwQkChMiA==" /></outline><outline text="Apply the principles of the spiritual warrior in your daily life. If you are a chip runner in a casino, be the very best, the most polite, the most skillful, the most cheerful chip runner they have ever seen."><sx:sync version="1" id="UrxUT80bm0+0ZL/49ZxB9A==" /></outline><outline text="If you are driving on the expressway, don't risk other peoples lives by being over confident and in a hurry."><sx:sync version="1" id="c0FCYvCuCkKdJDOQvOu+Nw==" /></outline><outline text="Be an empowered person"><outline text="Accept the present situation, however difficult, with a can-do attitude."><sx:sync version="1" id="Cfx3UIZHhUKnjHN98jVl3Q==" /></outline><outline text="Invest in yourself, your skills and abilities."><sx:sync version="1" id="b7JPA34V0UCoXT8rqFNiPQ==" /></outline><outline text="Help build a better world for future generations."><sx:sync version="1" id="3cwPGRhZ5kq8MLYUg/DXfA==" /></outline><outline text="Avoid forms of employment that are against your ethics and values."><sx:sync version="1" id="ojyXeoL+vkiypeIj97YFzA==" /></outline><outline text="Move forward with confidence and enthusiasm."><sx:sync version="1" id="dmR3uUxVNEC1fRzeeF74Ag==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="BvOafATgY0S8eVFoH39+GA==" /></outline><outline text="Even your next breath is not guaranteed. Therefore be the best that you can be in this moment."><sx:sync version="1" id="3TijG5QbPk29A473S2jyzQ==" /></outline><outline text="Your actions may not turn out as expected. Despite your best efforts, your actions may fail. That's not up to you."><sx:sync version="1" id="ipWyP9zZ+EKsXMkmlydX2Q==" /></outline><outline text="But you have control over your intentions. You can do your best to make a positive contribution. Your smile makes a difference. Your prayers make a difference."><sx:sync version="1" id="5GGn6rNWZkuV7jM52ObyAQ==" /></outline><outline text="In the words of Mother Teresa, &quot;Give the world the best you have and it may never be enough. Give your best anyway.&quot; "><sx:sync version="1" id="qovMHfuxe0ellzo0nv0+Xg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="7gt7ayvOg0GcdfShFH4PDw==" /></outline><outline text="Trust that you have enough / Serve the poor"><outline text="On the surface, it appears that selfish actions bring happiness."><sx:sync version="1" id="eTILB6pM8U27NA9q26NOQA==" /></outline><outline text="However, if you observe carefully and honestly, you will eventually realize that selfish actions provide, at best, a shallow version of happiness."><sx:sync version="1" id="OZakda9F40q/JTOY2f0mpg==" /></outline><outline text="It may take many life experiences before you are convinced that selfish actions are ultimately not satisfying. I mean, it's okay but isn't there something more, something better?"><sx:sync version="1" id="MnM0UZjd8k+NqNYMOtBqRA==" /></outline><outline text="If your life seems to have no meaning, try helping others. "><sx:sync version="1" id="hFHLXDv+XUeELpgDZnEqtA==" /></outline><outline text="Have faith that the universe is taking care of you. Consider how much money and resources you really need."><sx:sync version="1" id="6idUxMD0wUWxHlNbK1AYuw==" /></outline><outline text="Give excess wealth to the poor. Ask yourself, &quot;Is saving money for my imaginary future more important than helping people who are suffering now?&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="7R8hXg9jOEmcp3UaiTT6dQ==" /></outline><outline text="However, don't create a new ego identity as a noble person who serves the poor. Don't tell anyone. Let it be a secret between you and God."><sx:sync version="1" id="sekLnpPus0+fD2DejlE1Ig==" /></outline><outline text="Consider getting rid of possessions that you are most attached to. Nobody says freedom is going to be easy."><sx:sync version="1" id="17mJNjXhY064j8bNPL5wJA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="z6JxbIGbgEmrQwe9p4RbUQ==" /></outline><outline text="Sorrow is the ultimate catalyst"><outline text="At some point, the very thing you don't want to happen, happens. Every person will surely encounter painful difficulties, unacceptable events that appear to be complete disasters."><sx:sync version="1" id="rQgRhAD6DUSlIGl9Vu6l4Q==" /></outline><outline text="From the physical perspective, there is no way to deal with such experiences. When the worst possible thing happens, you are helpless. Normal thought processes and strategies are futile. Your normal view of reality is shattered and falls away."><sx:sync version="1" id="tb5FSOGyC06KyuMfB3c6wg==" /></outline><outline text="When all hope is lost, when you are facing an abyss of despair, there is a chance to access another reality. The primal knowledge from millions of past lifetimes and future lifetimes is trying to break through. In your broken condition, if you fearlessly abandon yourself into the unknown, you will absolutely know there is something greater. You will find yourself calling out to this Something Greater with your entire being."><sx:sync version="1" id="GaB/gXz980eoK8D1jXnQrA==" /></outline><outline text="At these times, Amma's advice is helpful, &quot;Cry out to your God. Call out from the bottom of your heart with all your might, What use is this life? How can I live without you? Where are you? Come before me right now! What use is this life without knowing you?&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="73w9hxgHDkm+yzB5G66fzQ==" /></outline><outline text="When you call out in complete sorrow, the entire universe bows down to this depth of prayer and concentration. It awakens the redemptive power of God's love, the Light more powerful than any darkness, the peace beyond understanding."><sx:sync version="1" id="bIlupEvQ0EeelS7ry/Mrew==" /></outline><outline text="In this way, sorrow can be the catalyst that brings you closer to the indescribable and indestructible Divine Reality."><sx:sync version="1" id="Y2lxaJh5NU+gotcU0X4Eag==" /></outline><outline text="In the words of Neem Karoli, &quot;I love sorrow. It brings me closer to God.&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="h3btQGKOIkmQoXdwGzY2FQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="wWBRregeGk2a1aa1X5evnw==" /></outline><outline text="Accept everything with love and gratitude"><outline text="It is the nature of life to have many problems."><sx:sync version="1" id="vrSjYL/fZE+DgFOFoyiV+A==" /></outline><outline text="Know that there are angelic beings watching over you. These beings fully understand everything about your situation. They are filled with unbearable love and compassion for you. They are cheering for you, praying for you, loving you. They know how hard it is to live in this beautiful and broken world."><sx:sync version="1" id="xlRFkF79N0KKVBzMbOeXJA==" /></outline><outline text="So relax. Be optimistic in spite of the problems. Don't worry. Don't brood over the past. Love and accept yourself as you are now. Have compassion for yourself."><sx:sync version="1" id="F5g1nDzLjEqqDal30kcThA==" /></outline><outline text="Whatever difficulties you face, whatever mental and physical defects you have, remain peaceful inside."><sx:sync version="1" id="/RYyGOQ8zUSnJ1oYxjc/1Q==" /></outline><outline text="Remind yourself, &quot;The creative power of the universe gave me this experience, and so it must be good for me, it must be for my purification and spiritual upliftment. Through this experience, I am fulfilling a difficult part of my destiny. So that's good, that much karma is paid off!&quot;"><sx:sync version="1" id="FS0+B+xGEEGSqFdYmjzN/Q==" /></outline><outline text="Always be enthusiastic and optimistic, even when facing death."><sx:sync version="1" id="jo4NDHTz50CIDXdbhWjRjg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="LMBrPh0TtU2hXzSOZCPagA==" /></outline><outline text="Thoughts create reality"><outline text="Every thought contributes to the overall mental atmosphere of the earth."><sx:sync version="1" id="/pT70E1BL0aWd5zYM+jT/w==" /></outline><outline text="All our thoughts go into the pipeline to be manifested later."><sx:sync version="1" id="LRRXyQWZhESf8RgjSSsEJA==" /></outline><outline text="Therefore don't allow negative thoughts to reside in your mind."><sx:sync version="1" id="NCkYOx1UYkqckZOGCZS0Pw==" /></outline><outline text="Train your mind to go to your highest thoughts and avoid every kind of negativity. This training will serve you well when difficult situations arise."><sx:sync version="1" id="F2CHX1XPGEinJEfgxGX3zg==" /></outline><outline text="Never doubt the immense power of truth and the human spirit."><sx:sync version="1" id="HRAWtKQov0C3Fpl8Q3K2/g==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="gjaX9SJfwkmQwvEgT3F6lw==" /></outline><outline text="Confront core challenges"><outline text="What are the crucial challenges you face?"><sx:sync version="1" id="CQDuAhp97UqvGQOWVQHgpw==" /></outline><outline text="What situations make you unhappy, tense, upset, or worried? Identify them specifically."><sx:sync version="1" id="olksal8WdkeLhbesuNlJ7A==" /></outline><outline text="Make an all-­out effort to confront these challenges head­-on with courage, determination, enthusiasm, and creativity."><sx:sync version="1" id="ZELM/nItEUWldoG9vZkxXg==" /></outline><outline text="What are your strong desires? Know that if these desires are fulfilled, you may end up enslaved to the situation that you created. Eventually you will want to get out. You will develop a strong desire for freedom."><sx:sync version="1" id="QvAWH1JjQkmYAW6ER5kRFw==" /></outline><outline text="To summarize, those who are enslaved want to be free. And those who are free want to be enslaved."><sx:sync version="1" id="ILG9Sw8Jbk6wwwPkP4Q9Lw==" /></outline><outline text="We are attracted toward the very things that make us suffer. That's our nature."><sx:sync version="1" id="E10Uhdzc7ku8EBzKHM4UjQ==" /></outline><outline text="When you were in the realm of pure spirit, in the unmanifested state before you were born into this life, you knew in general the types of experiences and challenges you would face. And now that you are here, are you ready to face the challenges? Sooner or later, you will have no choice but to confront them. Do you want to go for it now? Or wait until later?"><sx:sync version="1" id="Q5SrK3iPQky53hNAYat7nA==" /></outline><outline text="As a spiritual warrior, you already know the answer:"><outline text="Starting now, call out to your Spiritual Master and all your Spirit Allies to help you confront every challenge head on, using the principles explained above."><sx:sync version="1" id="+Qj2g8rsdEW4rBsEMO59hQ==" /></outline><outline text="In every moment, let your every thought be so loving and innocent, and your every action be so selfless and compassionate, so that when it is time for you to leave this world, you will be a hero going home."><sx:sync version="1" id="OR1GIBeJLkS/vojz3N2wfg==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="EZxUSPjV50OvgBwfmrDggA==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="x+CUqYo4n0GoxWXrvbvgAg==" /></outline><outline text="What is a spiritual warrior?"><outline text="Rules for a spiritual warrior"><outline text="There are no rules or formulas for a spiritual warrior."><sx:sync version="1" id="PCeUOfGLuUihNJvs9GNwfA==" /></outline><outline text="You can be a spiritual warrior in any situation, in any kind of work, anywhere."><sx:sync version="1" id="ASSendNteka1JSWotfc9RA==" /></outline><outline text="The spiritual path is equally available to all, regardless of credentials or dark personal history."><sx:sync version="1" id="lgZH3Ne0NEGD9nBPaAGDTQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="eBMAZnDjcEihhl3qpff/SQ==" /></outline><outline text="The spiritual warrior is one who declares all-out war on the thought patterns in his or her own mind that block the joy of human experience."><sx:sync version="1" id="gM2xlSXIJ0+sugalgoAsjw==" /></outline><outline text="Ultimately, the spiritual warrior comes to realize that concepts such as &quot;myself&quot; and &quot;others&quot;, and any concepts that divide, don't make sense. There is no enemy to fight against and defeat. There is nothing to seek and nothing to find. The search comes to an end where it started, inside your own self. "><sx:sync version="1" id="UMNsrgGO+Eao7AbMdWgCXg==" /></outline><outline text="&quot;In your own Self, you are the wanderer, the exile, the homecoming and the home. Oneself is all there is.&quot; - Anandamayi Ma"><sx:sync version="1" id="b6e9Esm9nEaItGCrGtO7mQ==" /></outline><outline text="The spiritual warrior knows everything is perfect as is..."><sx:sync version="1" id="rxavZfWooUe0ac1KW/ZONg==" /></outline><outline text="...and knows everything is screwed up and broken..."><sx:sync version="1" id="hoeu0OqU7UOh8wGZnATj3A==" /></outline><outline text="...and is okay with that"><sx:sync version="1" id="KqAUWvDxGkmG3YKDzbMLyA==" /></outline><outline text="...and is not okay with that"><sx:sync version="1" id="di8hw3EKdUCrfWxhhsB+AQ==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="BfyIjkSb00SHzjTpdWqqLA==" /></outline><outline text="Sources and inspirations"><outline text="Please forgive me for arrogantly and audaciously pretending to understand anything."><sx:sync version="1" id="bP7KtlOQRk6L2OStyiU9vQ==" /></outline><outline text="Mata Amritanandamayi Devi, aka Amma - 1953-"><sx:sync version="1" id="PBE+W0Fe9UOoZOBkc4F8Ag==" /></outline><outline text="Neem Karoli Baba, aka Maharaji - c. 1900 -1973"><sx:sync version="1" id="wyplAsJOO0Sk0PM0+qOcbw==" /></outline><outline text="Anandamayi Ma - 1896 -1982"><sx:sync version="1" id="BXQBlKOpmkOMEeJG/4jq2g==" /></outline><outline text="Nisargadatta Maharaj - 1897-1981"><sx:sync version="1" id="vQQVgGIyj0275Ynr2P3W2Q==" /></outline><outline text="Mother Teresa of Calcutta - 1910 - 1997"><sx:sync version="1" id="vMcuRu2EKku+u8x3SPPgeQ==" /></outline><outline text="Rumi, aka Jalal ad-Din Muhammad Rumi - 1207-1273"><sx:sync version="1" id="LWsABjnme0eT/yO2cyFYUA==" /></outline><outline text="Grandfather David Monongye - c. 1870 -1987"><sx:sync version="1" id="0ntk/ZJDTE6JR1f0p9d+aQ==" /></outline><outline text="Rolling Thunder, aka John Pope - 1916 -1997"><sx:sync version="1" id="eyoZwDPpF0yjwHc0hU7o/A==" /></outline><outline text="Carlos Castenada - 1925 -1998"><sx:sync version="1" id="8gTWcCe9UEazfAmidhrwTA==" /></outline><outline text="The Seth Material by Jane Roberts"><sx:sync version="1" id="UOtWW+qY4U+5ZJxYdPDjwA==" /></outline><outline text="The Art of Stalking Parallel Perception: The Living Tapestry of Lujan Matus by Lujan Matus"><sx:sync version="1" id="UDXN6ccVPkicH67UQHJp1A==" /></outline><outline text="Cutting through Spiritual Materialism by Chogyam Trungpa"><sx:sync version="1" id="tKYjW+fbDESPtevQK8qhmA==" /></outline><outline text="The Four Agreements by Don Miguel Ruiz"><sx:sync version="1" id="/khZm7nB0ECHEMIgm0OoTg==" /></outline><outline text="Wynton Marsalis - Jazz - Episode 1, documentary by Ken Burns"><sx:sync version="1" id="qmab7sImOUeCrDSKOayFOg==" /></outline><outline text="George Monbiot, The Guardian - 1/29/2024"><outline text="https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2024/jan/29/donald-trump-americans-us-culture-republican"><sx:sync version="1" id="l+5Ul/3Hj0G6ZJ1bTwtc3w==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="AW904mY/W0iNsckF0uCi4Q==" /></outline><outline text="Angelic Beings and Mountain Spirits, available telepathically in the Dreamtime"><sx:sync version="1" id="5Flh/3P3BE22/W26ng9dLw==" /></outline><outline text="If I have made any plagiarism violations, please notify me so that I can give credit or make corrections."><sx:sync version="1" id="HphqlnSaXkmuw3GpCHY8ww==" /></outline><sx:sync version="1" id="1GmWOE/DqES7dIrXZdIymA==" /></outline></body></opml>
